          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "As the GOP races to try to install Amy Barrett to the Supreme Court before the election, Joe Biden and most competitive Democratic Senate candidates — other than one — are running away from queries about whether they would support expanding the court.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
